{
  "_description": "Phase 1.5 knob-combination sweep. Each combo = a tuple of (knob, value) writes applied as a single cell. Five blocks: (A) 8 default agent arms from agent/src/action_grid_default.json [validation], (B) 3x3 CPU_FREQ x GPU_FREQ grid [main interaction test], (C) 3x3 CPU_FREQ x CPU_UNCORE grid [Phase 0 said uncore is HARMFUL on stream/osu but USEFUL on cpu-dgemm — tests whether keeping uncore high while dropping CPU is safe], (D) 2x2 GPU_FREQ x PERF_FACTOR [redundancy check: are these two GPU levers complementary or duplicates?], (E) 2x2 CPU_FREQ x CPU_POWER_LIMIT [redundancy check on the CPU side]. Total 34 combos per benchmark. See docs/phase1_5-combo-design.md.",
